    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在这款心理恐怖游戏中探索黑暗的谜团</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因令人毛骨悚然的超自然传闻而被吸引，超自然侦探哈里·沃尔特斯来到了废弃的吉尔曼家族老宅。四年前，这个家族神秘失踪，哈里开始揭开隐藏的线索，却逐渐被卷入致命的秘密之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能解开吉尔曼家族的谜团，还是真相将永远尘封？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286560/extras/f46779a29c86b57cac19ab7c2f0000af.poster.avif?t=1744938048\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286560/extras/f46779a29c86b57cac19ab7c2f0000af.webm?t=1744938048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286560/extras/f46779a29c86b57cac19ab7c2f0000af.mp4?t=1744938048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸式心理恐怖</strong>：体验扣人心弦的第一人称恐怖，时刻让你紧张不安。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>调查过往人生</strong>：挖掘尘封的记忆和诡异线索，揭开吉尔曼家族的命运之谜。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>解谜逃生</strong>：克服重重挑战，逃离无休止的恐怖。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>复古PSX美学</strong>：享受像素化的复古画面，增添恐怖氛围。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战斗或逃生</strong>：应对潜伏的威胁，选择战斗、躲藏或逃跑。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏时长</strong>：约120分钟</p>",
